commit.message: Fixed switch syntax error flagged by cppcheck
Correct the exception type raised by the finally block

Add let-operator to safely close DB

This can be used as a convenience, instead of having to manually call
`db_close` or remember to set up the close in some other way.
Fixed call to final aggregate function when no step function was called
Fixed missing GC registration of init values in aggregate functions
Switched to equivalent MIT license for proper SPDX identifier
Fixed incorrect required minimum OCaml version
Added support for const char strings in stubs

Merge pull request #46 from kumanna/master

Minor documentation typo and fix
